{
  "stem": "13313.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was able to, somehow, find it and keep it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and-- and--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe it was Coltex.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know the reason.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "C-O-L-T-E-X.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For a little while, we went under that name, just when the things got rougher towards the end of that two-year transitional period.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were no direct persecutions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That phase-- during that phase, there were no deportations yet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- so-- as I-- after the war, I studied this whole phenomenon of anti-Semitic persecution quite-- quite in depth.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It became one of my main subjects of interest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I spent a lot of time on that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I then studied, and I discovered that throughout the whole Christian era, whenever Jews are persecuted and put in ghettos and isolated, that it was always a Jewish reaction to apply towards persecution what was called the policy of accommodation.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was a traditional reaction by Jewish communities through their leadership.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This worked because it had never really been the official policy of the church or any government to completely destroy or annihilate the Jews.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were supposed to be persecuted, yes, to be deprived of certain occupations, herded into certain areas, extra tax imposed on them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it was never the policy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when this went on, the general Jewish reaction being so outnumbered was-- was to give in, kind of cooperate.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, that-- it would bend with the wind because it will blow over eventually, which it always did.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there was no-- and the leadership, that was the policy of the leadership.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just do what is being asked, and you'll be OK.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the general reaction.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Was that your father's point of view?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
